{"tid":2265173,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"陳虹秀：律政司要求沈小民法官就暴動案作呈述以便提上訴","createTime":"2020-10-31T08:13:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-31T08:30:09.000Z","uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c5a87f7a8331b4221b69fb1b9699a49b230637bb","tid":2265173,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T08:13:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1557665-20201031.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1557665-20201031.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=DHxvyfXarR7adKHN0Usak4%2FGH25nCqGTJutLbOxS7Ms%3D&h=44039bd7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1557665-20201031.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=8d6343f4\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1557665-20201031.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n香港社會工作者總工會理事陳虹秀早前獲撤銷暴動控罪，她在社交網站上載，律政司早前向區域法院法官沈小民發出的信件，律政司要求沈小民，作出案件呈述，以便律政司司長提出上訴。<br />\n<br />\n信件於本月5日發出，律政司表示不服裁定，認為法律觀點有錯誤，包括法官在裁定陳虹秀暴動罪表面證據不成立時，裁決是否屬於任何明理、妥為顧及考慮因素並發出適當指示的法官，都不可能達致的結論。<br />\n<br />\n律政司向法官申請，要求作出及簽署案件呈述，列明作出裁定的事實及理由，以便律政司司長可向上訴法庭提出上訴。<br />\n<br />\n同案另外7名被告，沈小民今日頒下判案書，裁定7人暴動罪不成立，其中一名被告被加控管有攻擊性武器亦脫罪。本台正向律政司查詢，是否會就案件提出上訴。"},{"pid":"524163cc68db04c421b43e87ab593406d394a6ca","tid":2265173,"uid":239392,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T08:18:55.000Z","msg":"死咬唔放，亳無同理心，正仆街。"},{"pid":"16a0a09a8a339b602a41e634f5b20ea053c6e207","tid":2265173,"uid":71092,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T08:19:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a32e788742feecd1093f1c62cc329065d205804","tid":2265173,"uid":32221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"524163cc68db04c421b43e87ab593406d394a6ca","tid":2265173,"uid":239392,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T08:18:55.000Z","msg":"死咬唔